<p>It&#039;s always something, and thankfully John and Dave are always here to help. This week we share some advice about geotagging your photos when shooting with a non-geo-smart DSLR camera. Then some talk about how to format Flash drives, and lots, lots more. It&#039;s always a blast &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt; you always learn at least 5 new things each and every time you get together with John and Dave.Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
